text: Thoriq Husler (19 April 1963 - 24 December 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was born in Palopo, Indonesia. He was the Regent of the East Luwu Regency from 2016 until his death. Husler died on 24 December 2020 in Makassar, Indonesia from COVID-19 at the age of 57.Bupati Lutim Terpilih Thoriq Husler Meninggal Dunia Akibat COVID-19 ==References== Category:1963 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Indonesia Category:Indonesian politicians
